<p>worn right off &amp; they let the water in. They are issuing passes for Warloy we are quite close to her.<br/>Feel very much better today  those pills seem to have done me the world of good.<br/>15th . Pretty busy today for I am Batt. Orderly Sergt, &amp; in a camp there are so many things for one to look after. Had another meeting of the Sergts last night &amp; the Mess is to be opened tonight &amp; a good job too  Most of the boys were pretty full last night.<br/>Heavy frost this morning but the sun is struggling to show itself for a while hope he gets out<br/>Very heavy sick parade some of them with nothing at all the matter with them at the present time we have a terrible lot of malingerers</p>
